          color: theme.colorScheme.primary.withOpacity(0.8),
          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(20)),
      child: Text(genre,
          style: const TextStyle(
              color: Colors.white, fontSize: 12, fontWeight: FontWeight.bold)),
    );
  }
}

